:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efd3e82a9a5bef30109600069c37e1b76b2de20d","tid":2081377,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"辯方申請討回訟費，裁判官稱被告在警誡下只說「好激氣」，而無解釋自己行為出於自衛，屬自招嫌疑，故拒批訟費。<br />\n<br />\n咁都自招嫌疑？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160602/19637564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160602%2F19637564&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFmztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=4d037b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160602%2F19637564&h=5cb0893f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160602/19637564</a><br />\n法官張慧玲於判詞指，上訴人劉子安（圖）被捕後保持緘默及在審訊中不作供，並不算自招嫌疑。至於原審裁判官另指上訴人沒有預先向控方披露開脫性證據，屬伏擊手段，故不應獲全數訟費，張官亦不認同。張官指原審時控方只謂如事先獲得影片或不繼續檢控，非如律政司代表在上訴時「事後孔明」稱必會終止檢控。對辯方不先將影片交控方，以免警員修補證供錯漏，張官亦認為有理據。"},{"pid":"e6a079e29acf7ee3a7f29805ae7f6a3411baee85","tid":2081377,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"保持緘默=自招嫌疑<br />\n香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6475a01309d46cea7c4e6be502fa06ffe1fafedb","tid":2081377,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6a079e29acf7ee3a7f29805ae7f6a3411baee85","tid":2081377,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"保持緘默=自招嫌疑<br />\n香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:06:12.000Z","msg":"話就話上級法院的判決對下級法院有約束力<br />\n但法官鳩判冇後果 黑警鳩拉冇後果<br />\n呢d就係叫約束力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}